description: For delicious classic comfort cuisine with a nutritious organic twist, you definitely wanna check out MaMa Dogs Catering. This family-run truck is serving up incredibly tasty burgers, hot dogs, tacos, and more, all made with the highest quality ingredients, and it’s all “sweet, sassy, savory, and sizzlin hot!”Come on out to MaMa Dog’s or invite her to your next party, for a spread of delectable selections that you and your guests are sure to love.
name: MaMa Dogs Catering
